title: Out with the old, in with the new! Res Lease in Austin. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ["You can't miss this fantastic opportunity!", 'This superb 1 story 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the Westgate neighborhood, just minutes from downtown is waiting for you!', 'This house welcomes you to its spacious living room with skylights on the vaulted ceiling, and a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace.', 'The well-designed kitchen boasts a great U-layout, has plenty of storage in its pantry and an abundance of white cabinets, plus comes fully equipped with stainless appliances: electric range, dishwasher and refrigerator.', 'There is a wonderful family/ bonus room that comes complete with built-in shelves.', 'This can easily be used as a home office!', 'The primary bedroom has a ceiling-fan, walk-in closet, a fully renovated bathroom with single vanity, huge mirror and a tiled walk-in shower great for relaxing after a long day!', 'The additional bedrooms share a newly renovated bathroom with a shower/tub combo.', "Don't forget to check out the amazing backyard surrounded by trees, with a covered terrace ready to be enjoyed with your loved ones!", 'Tour and apply to this one before it’s gone!', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 9253305)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
